{
    "swagger": "2.0",
    "info": {
        "description": "## API 响应\n\n当请求参数错误时，状态码为 `400`，payload 为：\n\n```json\n{\n    \"err\": \"ERR_INVAL_ARGS\",\n    \"msg\": \"detailed error\"\n}\n```\n\n其余情况状态码均为 `200`。当请求发生错误时，返回：\n\n```json\n{\n    \"err\": \"ERR_XXX (见接口文档)\",\n    \"msg\": \"detailed error (or null)\"\n}\n```\n\n当请求成功时，返回：\n\n```json\n{\n    \"data\": {\n        // ...\n    }\n}\n```\n\n\n\u003c!-- BEGIN ERROR --\u003e\n\n## 错误码\n\n### Universal errors\n\n`ERR_INVAL_ARGS`: The request body is invalid\n\n### Account related errors\n\n`ERR_ACCOUNT_SEND_TOO_OFTEN`: Send activation email too many times\n\n`ERR_ACCOUNT_INVALID_EMAIL`: The email is invalid\n\n`ERR_ACCOUNT_REGISTERED`: The email is already registered\n\n`ERR_ACCOUNT_NOT_ACTIVATED`: The email is not activated\n\n`ERR_ACCOUNT_PASSWORD_WEAK`: The password is too weak\n\n`ERR_ACCOUNT_USERNAME_EXISTS`: The username has already registered\n\n\u003c!-- END ERROR --\u003e",
        "title": "YARD API v1",
        "contact": {},
        "version": "1.0"
    },
